               <p>MARY SMITH. I am a <rs id="t18301028-132-viclabel736" type="occupation">widow</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301028-132-victim1139 t18301028-132-viclabel736"></join>. On the 24th of September I had been washing - I hung the property stated in my passage, near <placeName id="t18301028-132-crimeloc737">Chancery lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18301028-132-crimeloc737" type="placeName" value="Chancery lane"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18301028-132-crimeloc737" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301028-132-off734 t18301028-132-crimeloc737"></join>; I sent my boy out for some porter about half-past ten o'clock at night - the property was then safe; I had hung them up the last thing before I sat down to supper - the prisoner was taken within a few minutes; she was quite a stranger.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18301028-132-person1140">
                  ROBERT 
                  SMITH
